item.title: CVE-2023-32471|2024-08-02T15:18:37.608Z -- dell -- dell%20edge%20gateway%205200
item.description: Dell Edge Gateway BIOS, versions 3200 and 5200, contains an out-of-bounds read vulnerability. A local authenticated malicious user with high privileges could potentially exploit this vulnerability to read contents of stack memory and use this information for further exploits.
